{"tid":258394,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"如何解決好想我讀大學的老母","createTime":"2017-05-26T05:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T07:54:24.000Z","uid":74203,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9957721543290b802c8fa1084810ba5c321e531f","tid":258394,"uid":74203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:45:14.000Z","msg":"我入唔到嘛屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b9d376a1718dd62f74299c98467bad4f091ff8","tid":258394,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:46:48.000Z","msg":"解決不了問題所在<br />\n便解決提出問題的人"},{"pid":"1aa69b9819b0013a28ea005e793abc439c051fed","tid":258394,"uid":41742,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:47:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n<br />\n我表哥佢今年考DSE，琴日放榜 <br />\n佢考得唔係太好，又怕呀媽擔心 <br />\n呀媽一生人既夢想佢佢個仔入大學 <br />\n因為佢d親戚街坊都無仔女入到U <br />\n<br />\n今日一早番左屋企時，呀媽係咁問佢成績點，夠唔夠分, 可以入邊間U <br />\n表哥心情唔好，是撚但但同呀媽佢佢去讀藥劑， <br />\n之後請入房訓較(尋晚通左頂) <br />\n<br />\n表哥起左身，屙完屎之後出黎 <br />\n發現成家人都好開心，呀爸呀媽叫撚晒佢d親戚姑嫂話今晚出黎食飯 <br />\n同個仔興祝入到HKU讀藥劑 <br />\n<br />\n依個時候先知大撚獲 <br />\n表哥其實係去報IVE讀藥劑 <br />\n唔撚知邊個親戚街坊話係香港既大學，只有HKU有藥劑讀 <br />\n所以呀媽以為佢夠分入左HKU <br />\n<br />\n屌你 <br />\n我表哥頭sin打電話比我 <br />\n問我點做好........."},{"pid":"50cc22558ec86cbcbd13b0a114a3a76e1dcd871d","tid":258394,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>解決不了問題所在<br />\n便解決提出問題的人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e625bb1acdaa842f3611a4f113fefb1a1d04e9","tid":258394,"uid":4000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>解決不了問題所在<br />\n便解決提出問題的人</blockquote><br />\nChing Ho ball <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no